N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 213.9 - Commission access to records and exhibitions

State Regulations
A promoter of professional wrestling shall make its records
available to the Commission for review and copying at any time and without
limitation. An inspector, deputy or other Commission employee shall be
permitted entry to any event at any time without limitation. Notes
